{"tid":1052061,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[三國/華南史] 士燮算唔算係被嚴重低估o既諸候?","createTime":"2019-03-08T05:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T18:10:35.000Z","uid":52349,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cb74aeb2997d082354b1242528d5c0bcbc88455a","tid":1052061,"uid":52349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"亂世之下統治交州40年,仲要無發生過大型戰亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n漢室(曹操) 封賜士燮「九錫、六佾之舞」<br />\n而係當代領得起九錫封賜,都係有能力稱王稱帝之人,例如:<br />\n<br />\n1.王莽被漢朝授九錫，王莽後篡漢建新朝。<br />\n2.曹操被漢朝授九錫，其子曹丕後篡漢建魏。<br />\n3. 孫權名義上降曹魏被授九錫，數年後稱帝建立東吳。<br />\n4司馬昭被曹魏授九錫，後來其子司馬炎建晉朝。<br />\n5.晉惠帝加趙王司馬倫九錫，司馬倫矯詔晉惠帝禪位，自稱皇帝。"},{"pid":"59172ccc415743d14ccd8612395540469aea5c6b","tid":1052061,"uid":40146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:01:39.000Z","msg":"對入面d人黎講亂世wfc<br />\n搞掂自己再算啦<br />\n咁偏遠"},{"pid":"ff5e7a7e93142c75968af702a85d6df6ae05140d","tid":1052061,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:04:45.000Z","msg":"交州咁Q遠, 冇人打佢<br />\n而且士燮係曹丞相加九錫<br />\n但係結果支持孫吳"},{"pid":"515561d72e44e4fd7f57009c556f5efb742dadeb","tid":1052061,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ff5e7a7e93142c75968af702a85d6df6ae05140d","tid":1052061,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:04:45.000Z","msg":"交州咁Q遠, 冇人打佢<br />\n而且士燮係曹丞相加九錫<br />\n但係結果支持孫吳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:07:30.000Z","msg":"東吳最近，一定係親東吳先嫁啦"},{"pid":"f03513acb8141e855b9ebe86d1973601b4cda8fb","tid":1052061,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:08:34.000Z","msg":"不漏洞奶"},{"pid":"8228ddba118ea496610b2a6d46a5adfb79e08892","tid":1052061,"uid":52349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59172ccc415743d14ccd8612395540469aea5c6b","tid":1052061,"uid":40146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:01:39.000Z","msg":"對入面d人黎講亂世wfc<br 